"I'm fine..."replied Windlord.

Windlord had been injured and he needed CR  but he liked to be sure 
that his friend Aerotaur and the Lady (Empath) were all right. Condor 
was helping Windlord to walk.

Windlord opened his com in all Maximals "Aerotaur, Empath... Are you 
all right?"
